<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Interest - Artkya</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite alternate;
        }
        
        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #5a6c7d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .confirmation-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #d4edda 100%);
            color: #155724;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .confirmation-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .confirmation-title::before {
            content: "‚úÖ";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .confirmation-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .inquiry-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #155724;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .artwork-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .artwork-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .artwork-title::before {
            content: "üé®";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        
        .artwork-image {
            max-width: 250px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .artwork-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #bbdefb 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #2196f3;
        }
        
        .next-steps-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #0d47a1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .next-steps-title::before {
            content: "üìã";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .step-item {
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: #0d47a1;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 40px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .step-item:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 12px;
            background: #2196f3;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .timeline-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff9800;
        }
        
        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #e65100;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .timeline-title::before {
            content: "‚è∞";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .timeline-text {
            color: #e65100;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ffcc02;
        }
        
        .contact-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e5f5 0%, #e1bee7 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border-left: 5px solid #9c27b0;
        }
        
        .contact-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #4a148c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .contact-text {
            color: #4a148c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .contact-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .contact-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #9c27b0;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .contact-button:hover {
            background: #7b1fa2;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.3);
        }
        
        .contact-button.secondary {
            background: white;
            color: #9c27b0;
            border: 2px solid #9c27b0;
        }
        
        .contact-button.secondary:hover {
            background: #9c27b0;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .support-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .support-email {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #74b9ff;
        }
        
        .footer-bottom {
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #34495e;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #95a5a6;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .artwork-image {
                max-width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
            }
            
            .contact-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .contact-button {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
            }
            
            .social-links a {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">ARTKYA</div>
            <div class="success-icon">üéâ</div>
            <div class="header-title">Thank You for Your Interest!</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{customer.firstName}}!</div>
            
            <p class="intro-text">
                Thank you so much for your interest in our artwork! We're thrilled that you've chosen to reach out to us. Your inquiry is very important to us, and we're excited to help you find the perfect piece for your collection.
            </p>

            <!-- Confirmation Section -->
            <div class="confirmation-section">
                <div class="confirmation-title">Your Inquiry Has Been Successfully Received</div>
                <p class="confirmation-text">
                    We've received all your details and our art specialists are already reviewing your request.
                </p>
                
                <div class="inquiry-details">
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Inquiry Date:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{orderDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Inquiry Time:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{orderTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Your Email:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{customer.email}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Reference:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">ART-{{orderDate}}-{{orderTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Artwork Section -->
            {{#if artwork.title}}
            <div class="artwork-section">
                <div class="artwork-title">Your Artwork of Interest</div>
                {{#if artwork.image}}
                <img src="{{artwork.image}}" alt="{{artwork.title}}" class="artwork-image">
                {{/if}}
                <div class="artwork-name">{{artwork.title}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <!-- Timeline Section -->
            <div class="timeline-section">
                <div class="timeline-title">Expected Response Time</div>
                <div class="timeline-text">
                    <strong>We will contact you within 24 hours</strong><br>
                    Our team typically responds within 2-6 hours during business hours.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Next Steps -->
            <div class="next-steps">
                <div class="next-steps-title">What Happens Next?</div>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li class="step-item">Our art specialist will review your inquiry and the artwork details</li>
                    <li class="step-item">We'll contact you via email or phone to discuss your preferences</li>
                    <li class="step-item">We'll provide detailed information about pricing, availability, and condition</li>
                    <li class="step-item">If you decide to proceed, we'll arrange secure payment and delivery options</li>
                    <li class="step-item">Your artwork will be carefully packaged and shipped to your address</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Section -->
            <div class="contact-section">
                <div class="contact-title">Have Questions? We're Here to Help!</div>
                <p class="contact-text">
                    If you have any immediate questions or need to update your inquiry, don't hesitate to reach out to us directly.
                </p>
                <div class="contact-buttons">
                    <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}?subject=Inquiry About {{artwork.title}}" class="contact-button">
                        üìß Email Us
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}" class="contact-button secondary">
                        üåê Visit Website
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="support-text">Questions about your inquiry?</div>
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-email">{{supportEmail}}</a>
                
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}">üè† Visit Our Website</a>
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/gallery">üé® View Gallery</a>
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/about">‚ÑπÔ∏è About Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Artkya. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This confirmation was sent to {{customer.email}} regarding your art inquiry.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">
                    You're receiving this email because you submitted an inquiry through our website. 
                    If you have any concerns, please contact us immediately.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>